== 延伸 ==
由于1989年胡耀邦的逝世导致[[六四事件|六四事件]]的发生，使得胡耀邦在[[中国|中国]]国内成为政治敏感人物之一，在中国大陆高调纪念胡耀邦不被当局允许<ref>{{cite news|title=一周网络热贴|url=http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/vt-04162014151811.html|newspaper=自由亚洲电台|date=2014-04-16|accessdate=2014-11-24|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924134058/http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/vt-04162014151811.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=胡耀邦诞辰99周年 网民谨慎纪念(图)|url=http://www.secretchina.com/news/14/11/22/560515.html?%E8%83%A1%E8%80%80%E9%82%A6%E8%AF%9E%E8%BE%B099%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%20%E7%BD%91%E6%B0%91%E8%B0%A8%E6%85%8E%E7%BA%AA%E5%BF%B5(%E5%9B%BE)|newspaper=看中国|date=2014-11-22|accessdate=2014-11-24|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924100011/http://www.secretchina.com/news/14/11/22/560515.html?%E8%83%A1%E8%80%80%E9%82%A6%E8%AF%9E%E8%BE%B099%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%20%E7%BD%91%E6%B0%91%E8%B0%A8%E6%85%8E%E7%BA%AA%E5%BF%B5(%E5%9B%BE)|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该歌曲在部分场合也被用作歌颂[[教师|教师]]的歌曲<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.163.com/10/0608/04/68KL33S300014AED.html|title=好大一棵树 深情藏沃土|newspaper=网易新闻|date=2010-06-08|access-date=2014-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129114831/http://news.163.com/10/0608/04/68KL33S300014AED.html|archive-date=2014-11-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

